{
  "text": "Given r \u2208 Z >0 and \u03c4, \u03bb \u2208 R >0 with \u03c3 := \u03c4 \u2212 r\u03bb > 0, in [CITATION_1] we considered the Hirzebruch surface N determined by these numbers. N is the quotient",
  "correct_citation": {
